org.libav.avformat.bridge

Class AVStream54

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bridj.NativeObject
      • org.bridj.StructObject
        • org.libav.avformat.bridge.AVStream54
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bridj.NativeObjectInterface

    public class AVStream54
extends org.bridj.StructObject
    Mirror of the native AVStream struct for the libavformat v54.x.x. This class contains only the public API fields, the real AVStream struct is bigger. For details see the Libav documentation.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
